  <brief_title>Evaluation of ETC-1002 in Patients With Hypercholesterolemia and Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Placebo-Controlled, Randomized, Double-Blind, Parallel Group Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of ETC-1002 in Patients With Hypercholesterolemia and Hypertension</official_title>
